# Hermes Release Public Key (Ed25519)
#
# This is the trust root for bundle manifest signatures. The Rust updater
# embeds this key at compile time via include_str! and uses it to verify
# every release manifest's Ed25519 signature.
#
# Format: base64-encoded 32-byte Ed25519 public key on a single line.
#
# In CI builds, this file is populated by the release workflow from the
# HERMES_RELEASE_PUBLIC_KEY environment variable. For local development
# and testing, the build falls back to HERMES_RELEASE_PUBLIC_KEY if this
# file is empty or missing.
